snippet.title: Comeback - Jam Trailer
snippet.description:
https://guselect.itch.io/comeback

In a cold and empty world, only you and your peculiar light weapon can help you survive. Use it to trap enemies, kill them and return home.

Game made in 10 days for #coronajam
